[Car Tires Screech]

15:53.185 --> 15:55.881
I gave you the road.
Why don't you take it?

15:59.391 --> 16:01.222
Why don't you go?

16:34.193 --> 16:37.720
Oh, boy, you're beautiful.

16:49.842 --> 16:53.107
[Car Tires Screech]

16:53.178 --> 16:55.203
I don't believe it.

16:56.782 --> 16:58.716
I don't believe it.

17:09.560 --> 17:13.122
I'm in no mood to play games.
Let's go.

17:16.801 --> 17:19.635
[Honks Horn]

17:41.493 --> 17:45.020
Well, it's about time, Charlie!

17:46.532 --> 17:49.160
<i>[Horn Honks]</i>

17:54.206 --> 17:56.834
My God.

17:58.377 --> 18:00.311
Jesus.

18:09.655 --> 18:13.955
Come on, you miserable fathead.
Get that fat-ass truck out of my way.

18:22.534 --> 18:25.469
Well, I'm never going to
make that appointment now.

18:46.492 --> 18:48.517
You miserable...

19:02.341 --> 19:08.041
Okay. Okay.
You want to play games.

19:22.995 --> 19:26.123
[Laughing]

20:01.400 --> 20:07.236
<i>[Turns Radio On]</i>
<i>[Static, Country Tune, </i>
<i>Adjusting Station]</i>

21:25.617 --> 21:28.552
<i>~~ [Continues]</i>

21:55.814 --> 21:58.715
[Truck Horn Blasts]

21:58.784 --> 22:01.184
[Car Tires Screech]

22:01.253 --> 22:03.778
<i>~~ [Continues]</i>

22:12.164 --> 22:14.689
[Truck Horn]

22:35.721 --> 22:37.951
[Truck Horn]

23:04.883 --> 23:10.116
[Truck Horn]

23:26.138 --> 23:28.470
[Truck Horn]

23:30.609 --> 23:34.511
[Truck Horn]

23:56.134 --> 23:59.069
[Truck Horn]

24:04.276 --> 24:06.972
[Truck Horn]

24:30.368 --> 24:33.303
[Truck Horn]

25:30.262 --> 25:33.425
<i>~~ [Car Radio Playing]</i>

25:33.498 --> 25:35.432
<i>You all right, mister? </i>

25:35.500 --> 25:38.731
Uhh! [Coughing]

25:38.803 --> 25:42.762
Yeah. Yeah, except...

25:42.841 --> 25:45.776
Oh, my neck.
You got a whiplash,
probably.

25:45.844 --> 25:48.972
Yeah. It's all right.

25:51.016 --> 25:53.644
He's all right.

25:55.820 --> 25:57.754
What happened?

25:59.958 --> 26:03.724
That truck driver
tried to kill me.
Kill you? Go on!

26:03.795 --> 26:06.263
He chased me
down the mountain at...

26:06.331 --> 26:08.891
at nearly 90 miles an hour,
and I don't...

26:08.967 --> 26:12.801
don't know what else
you'd call it.
Tried to kill you.

26:12.871 --> 26:17.001
It sure looks like you got
whiplash, all right.
Oh, it's... it's, uh...

26:17.075 --> 26:19.566
You got the whiplash,
all right.
Oh, that's okay.

26:19.644 --> 26:21.578
Thank... It's okay.

26:21.646 --> 26:24.206
Anything I can do for you?
No, nothing. Thank you.

26:24.282 --> 26:26.341
That's okay.
Okay.

26:26.418 --> 26:29.717
<i>~~ [Car Radio</i>
<i>Continues Playing]</i>

26:29.788 --> 26:32.313
[Chuckling]

26:32.390 --> 26:35.086
Just a little whiplash is all.
[Chuckling]

27:21.106 --> 27:24.633
<i>[Chattering]</i>

27:27.746 --> 27:29.680
<i>What happened</i>
<i>out there, mister? </i>

27:29.748 --> 27:33.479
Can I use your
men's room, please?
Yeah. Through the door...

27:33.551 --> 27:36.486
on the right,
down the hall...

27:36.554 --> 27:38.988
turn left, second door.

28:34.479 --> 28:39.416
<i>[Mann's Voice]</i>
<i>Well, you never know. </i>
<i>You just never know. </i>

28:39.484 --> 28:42.578
<i>You just go along figuring</i>
<i>some things don't change, ever. </i>

28:42.654 --> 28:46.420
<i>Like being able to drive</i>
<i>on a public highway... </i>

28:46.491 --> 28:49.585
<i>without somebody trying</i>
<i>to murder you. </i>

28:49.661 --> 28:53.597
<i>And then one stupid thing</i>
<i>happens. </i>

28:53.665 --> 28:57.260
<i>Twenty, twenty-five minutes</i>
<i>out of your whole life... </i>

28:57.335 --> 29:01.669
<i>and all the ropes that kept you</i>
<i>hangin'in there get cut loose. </i>

29:01.740 --> 29:06.803
<i>And it's like, there you are, </i>
<i>right back in thejungle again. </i>

29:08.613 --> 29:12.379
<i>All right, boy, </i>
<i>it was a nightmare, </i>
<i>but it's over now. </i>

29:14.085 --> 29:16.519
<i>It's all over. </i>

29:37.575 --> 29:39.975
Are you all right?
Yeah, I'm fine.

29:40.044 --> 29:44.811
What happened out there?
Oh, just a slight
complication.

29:44.883 --> 29:48.319
Oh? Looked like a big
complication to me.

29:48.386 --> 29:53.187
<i>[Customers Laughing]</i>

32:13.464 --> 32:16.797
- [Silverware Clatters Loudly]
- Well, you ready to order now?

32:16.868 --> 32:19.029
Ahem. Yes. Heh heh.

32:19.103 --> 32:21.333
Yes, thank you. Um...

32:25.410 --> 32:27.970
Oh, I think I'll...

32:30.048 --> 32:31.845
Ahh.

32:31.916 --> 32:33.975
Just give me, um... um...

32:34.052 --> 32:37.215
Why don't you just give me
a Swiss cheese sandwich...

32:37.288 --> 32:40.655
- On rye. R-Y-E.
- Swiss cheese on rye.

32:40.725 --> 32:43.660
- All right.
- And could I have another
glass of water, please?

32:43.728 --> 32:46.891
- Oh, sure.
Another glass of water.
- Oh, uh, miss?

32:46.965 --> 32:49.695
- Do you have an aspirin?
- Aw, your head aches.

32:49.767 --> 32:51.860
Sure, I'll get you some aspirin.

33:06.150 --> 33:09.415
<i>[Mann's Voice]</i>
<i>All I did was pass this</i>
<i>stupid rig a couple of times... </i>

33:09.487 --> 33:12.581
<i>and he goes flyin'</i>
<i>off the deep end. </i>

33:12.657 --> 33:15.421
<i>He has to be crazy. </i>

33:15.493 --> 33:20.123
<i>Okay, so he's crazy. </i>
<i>What can I do about it? </i>

33:20.198 --> 33:23.634
<i>Find him a psychiatrist? </i>
<i>[Customers Laughing]</i>

33:23.701 --> 33:25.760
<i>[Exhaling] Oh, boy. </i>

34:11.983 --> 34:14.382
<i>Now wait a minute. </i>

34:14.452 --> 34:19.014
<i>Now wait just a minute. </i>
<i>All right, now, think. </i>

34:20.458 --> 34:24.326
<i>Okay, he's in here. </i>

34:24.395 --> 34:29.161
<i>Well, that doesn't mean</i>
<i>he intends to continue his... attack. </i>

34:29.233 --> 34:32.100
<i>It is lunchtime... </i>

34:32.170 --> 34:37.802
<i>and Chuck's Cafe may be</i>
<i>the only place to eat for miles around. </i>

34:37.875 --> 34:40.503
<i>Yeah. He probably</i>
<i>eats here all the time. </i>

34:40.578 --> 34:43.411
<i>He was just... </i>
<i>just moving too fast before... </i>

34:43.481 --> 34:47.417
<i>and he had to... slow down, </i>
<i>turn around, that's all. </i>

34:51.922 --> 34:53.857
<i>That's all. </i>

34:56.494 --> 34:58.485
<i>[Billiard Balls Clacking]</i>

34:58.563 --> 35:01.464
<i>Why didn't I leave right away</i>
<i>when I saw his truck outside? </i>

35:01.532 --> 35:04.558
<i>Then I'd know what</i>
<i>he intends to do. </i>

35:06.737 --> 35:10.332
<i>What if he followed me out, </i>
<i>started after me again? </i>

35:10.408 --> 35:12.342
<i>I'd be right back</i>
<i>where I started. </i>

35:12.410 --> 35:14.970
<i>Even if I got a lead, </i>
<i>he'd overtake me soon enough. </i>

35:15.046 --> 35:18.277
<i>He's got some... some... </i>
<i>some souped-up diesel. </i>

35:18.349 --> 35:21.079
<i>My-My car's just not</i>
<i>that powerful. I just... </i>

35:21.152 --> 35:24.349
<i>can't drive 80 and 90</i>
<i>miles an hour. </i>

35:24.422 --> 35:28.415
<i>As soon as I stopped concentrating, </i>
<i>I'd go back to 60 or 70</i>
<i>like I always do. </i>

35:28.493 --> 35:30.324
<i>It's a habit. </i>
<i>I can't help it. </i>

35:30.394 --> 35:34.091
<i>I ca... Take it easy. </i>

35:34.799 --> 35:38.792
<i>Just... take it easy. </i>

35:38.870 --> 35:40.804
<i>Maybe l... </i>

35:42.340 --> 35:46.037
<i>Maybe I should try</i>
<i>some kind of contact. </i>

35:46.110 --> 35:48.874
<i>[Customers Talking, Laughing]</i>
<i>I'd better do something. </i>

35:53.451 --> 35:55.612
<i>Look, mister, l... I'm sorry</i>
<i>if I irritated you. </i>

35:55.686 --> 36:00.020
<i>Why don't I buy you a beer</i>
<i>and get this straightened out? </i>

36:00.091 --> 36:01.956
<i>No. </i>

36:04.829 --> 36:07.992
<i>Look, mister, I'm sorry</i>
<i>if I irritated you, but... </i>

36:08.065 --> 36:09.999
<i>let me, uh... </i>

36:21.812 --> 36:26.647
There you are.
Anything else?
No, thank you.

36:26.717 --> 36:29.208
Uh...

36:29.287 --> 36:31.278
I'd like some ketchup.

36:54.045 --> 36:56.605
<i>What if I called</i>
<i>the local police? </i>

36:56.681 --> 36:59.377
<i>But then I'd have to</i>
<i>stay here, lose more time. </i>

36:59.450 --> 37:02.419
<i>What if he stayed too? </i>
<i>Actually talked</i>
<i>to the police himself? </i>

37:02.486 --> 37:04.215
<i>Naturally, </i>
<i>he'd deny everything. </i>

37:04.288 --> 37:08.281
<i>I've got to prove it. </i>
<i>None of these people</i>
<i>would back me up. </i>

37:08.359 --> 37:11.294
<i>The cops'd probably... </i>
<i>[Cash Register Rings]</i>

37:24.442 --> 37:27.240
<i>[Bell Rings, Door Closes]</i>

37:40.391 --> 37:42.484
<i>[Engine Starts]</i>

38:26.570 --> 38:30.506
<i>Okay... so now what? </i>
[Clears Throat]

39:28.065 --> 39:30.260
Look, uh...

39:31.902 --> 39:33.836
heh heh...

39:34.839 --> 39:38.605
- I want you to cut it out.
- What?

39:40.378 --> 39:43.313
Just-Just cut it out, okay?

39:46.650 --> 39:51.349
- Cut what out?
- Now, come on. I mean...

39:51.422 --> 39:55.449
please, l-l...
Let's not play games.

39:55.526 --> 39:59.587
- What the hell are you
talking about?
- I can call the police.

40:02.099 --> 40:06.593
- The police?
- You think that I won't?
You're wrong, mister.

40:06.670 --> 40:09.434
If you think you can
take that truck of yours...

40:09.507 --> 40:14.809
and use it as a murder weapon,
killing people on the highway,
well, you're wrong.

40:14.879 --> 40:18.872
<i>You've got another thing comin'. </i>
Man, you need help.

40:20.084 --> 40:22.609
Don't you tell me
I need help.

40:25.556 --> 40:28.184
Hey! Hey, hey, come on!

40:28.259 --> 40:30.124
Who the hell
do you think you are...

40:30.194 --> 40:33.391
- Knockin' my sandwich
outta my hand?
- You wanna fight, get outside.

40:33.464 --> 40:37.298
<i>- I don't wanna fight, </i>
<i>I wanna knock his head off. </i>
- You already hit him twice.

40:37.368 --> 40:40.337
<i>What more do you want? </i>
<i>Huh? Come on now. </i>

40:40.404 --> 40:43.339
<i>He's sick. Can't you see? </i>
<i>He ain't gonna fight no one. </i>

40:43.407 --> 40:47.173
That creep goes around,
knocks my sandwich outta my hand.

40:47.244 --> 40:49.178
I'll buy you
another sandwich.

40:49.246 --> 40:51.180
Come on, forget it.
No, forget it.

40:51.248 --> 40:53.648
- Forget it.
- I don't wanna stay
around here anyway.

40:53.717 --> 40:56.811
Let me buy you
a beer then, huh?

40:56.887 --> 40:58.821
I'll buy you a beer.

41:03.494 --> 41:05.519
Get out of here, huh?

41:05.596 --> 41:09.726
[Customers Murmuring]

41:16.874 --> 41:19.809
[Engine Starts, Gears Rattle]

41:49.373 --> 41:52.308
<i>[Truck Engine Starts]</i>

43:16.660 --> 43:20.096
[Engine Starts]

43:54.264 --> 43:57.199
[Chattering]

44:09.780 --> 44:13.546
[Kids Cheering]

44:13.617 --> 44:17.417
Yeah?
I'm sorry to bother you,
but I could use help.

44:17.488 --> 44:22.118
What kind of help?
I could use a push.
Damn thing overheated.

44:22.192 --> 44:24.285
Now I can't get her
started again.

44:24.361 --> 44:26.625
Why didn't you flag down
that truck?
What truck?

44:26.697 --> 44:30.292
The one that just
went by here.
I didn't notice.

44:30.367 --> 44:33.131
I must have been inside
tryin' to get that
piece of junk shakin'.

44:33.203 --> 44:35.797
Would you get off
the car?
How about it?

44:35.873 --> 44:40.139
Looks like I'd go
right underneath the bumper.
No.

44:40.210 --> 44:43.737
Hey, get off the car.
You're gonna get hurt there.

44:43.814 --> 44:47.147
Naw, you're all right.
Rodney, get down
from there.

44:47.217 --> 44:50.084
<i>You too, Shawn. </i>
<i>Come on, everybody! </i>
<i>Back on the bus! </i>

44:50.154 --> 44:52.748
Wait a minute!
Wait, l...

44:52.823 --> 44:57.055
<i>[Kids Chattering]</i>
Well, we'll see.

44:57.127 --> 44:59.925
<i>[Car Engine</i>
<i>Starts]</i>
[Chattering Continues]

45:14.845 --> 45:17.075
Come on. Come on.

45:38.335 --> 45:40.769
<i>[Kids Yelling]</i>

45:40.838 --> 45:44.934
Push! Push! Push!

45:45.008 --> 45:48.967
Push! Push! Push! Push!

45:49.046 --> 45:54.484
<i>Push! Push! </i>
<i>Push! Push! </i>

45:54.551 --> 45:59.614
<i>Push! Push! </i>
<i>Push! Push! </i>

45:59.690 --> 46:03.626
<i>Push! Push! </i>
<i>[Indistinct Yelling]</i>

46:04.828 --> 46:10.232
<i>Push! Push! Push! </i>

46:10.300 --> 46:15.533
[Laughing]

46:20.944 --> 46:22.935
He can't do it!

46:23.013 --> 46:26.312
You can't do it!
You can't do it!

46:26.383 --> 46:29.978
You can't do it!
You can't do it!

46:31.221 --> 46:34.088
[Yelling]

46:34.158 --> 46:37.616
Mr. Pfeiffer,
that guy's stuck too.

46:37.694 --> 46:39.958
Shit.

46:42.699 --> 46:44.724
<i>[Kid]</i>
<i>You can't do it! </i>

46:50.474 --> 46:54.001
Sorry, mister.
I coulda swore we were okay.

46:54.077 --> 46:58.013
I told you we were
gonna get hung up.
How 'bout
I give you a hand?

46:58.081 --> 47:00.811
Don't, don't,
don't sit on the hood.

47:00.884 --> 47:04.081
That hood'll dent.
I told the kids not
to get on the hood.

47:05.989 --> 47:09.083
Just, uh, see if you
can bounce it loose...

47:09.159 --> 47:11.593
and I'll, uh, uh...

47:13.497 --> 47:15.431
Just bounce it loose.

47:20.337 --> 47:24.740
[Engine Revving]

47:39.323 --> 47:44.659
<i>[Kids Yelling]</i>

47:54.204 --> 47:58.004
Hold it!

47:58.075 --> 48:00.407
[Exhales]

48:13.490 --> 48:15.583
Somethin' wrong?

48:18.095 --> 48:21.292
That bastard turned around
and came back.

48:21.365 --> 48:24.095
<i>[Bus Driver]</i>
<i>Is that the truck</i>
<i>you were askin'about? </i>

48:24.167 --> 48:28.263
<i>[Kids Laughing, Yelling]</i>

48:29.339 --> 48:32.775
Uh... get those kids
out of the way.

48:32.843 --> 48:35.607
What for?
Just get them off the road
and they'll be okay.

48:35.679 --> 48:38.045
They're all right.
They're not on the road.

48:38.115 --> 48:41.881
[Kids Yelling, Laughing]
Get, get back
in the bus. Please!

48:41.952 --> 48:43.715
Come on. Back in the bus!

48:43.787 --> 48:45.812
You're all right
right where you are...

48:45.889 --> 48:48.483
long as you stay
off the road.
Come on!

48:48.558 --> 48:52.494
- You're perfectly all right.
- Let's get back in the bus,
come on.

48:52.562 --> 48:55.531
Get off of the highway.
There's a truck coming.

48:55.599 --> 48:59.399
You must be
out of your brains!
Yeah! Yeah!

48:59.469 --> 49:02.870
Come on! Please!
Take your hands
off these...

49:02.940 --> 49:04.874
Get back in the bus!
Get your hands off him!

49:04.942 --> 49:07.809
Now, look, I know
how this must sound,
[Indistinct Yelling]

49:07.878 --> 49:10.813
But that man is crazy.
He's been trying to kill me.

49:10.881 --> 49:14.408
If I had to vote on who's crazy,
it'd be you.
<i>[Truck Engine Starts]</i>

49:14.484 --> 49:16.884
Uh, um...

49:16.954 --> 49:20.583
<i>[Kids Yelling]</i>
When I bust 'em loose,
pull it back.

49:30.600 --> 49:32.363
Now! Now!

49:34.638 --> 49:37.573
<i>[Kids Chattering]</i>

51:05.328 --> 51:09.697
[Whistle Blowing]

51:09.766 --> 51:12.667
[Crossing Bell Ringing]

51:22.412 --> 51:25.540
[Whistle Blows]
[Bell Ringing]

51:36.626 --> 51:38.856
<i>[Thud]</i>

51:40.197 --> 51:42.131
Hey! Hey!

51:42.199 --> 51:45.464
<i>[Crossing Bell</i>
<i>Continues Ringing]</i>

51:58.281 --> 52:00.181
Hey, stop!

52:04.754 --> 52:07.188
Hey!

52:13.163 --> 52:15.597
Hey!

52:21.071 --> 52:23.369
[Tires Screeching]

52:38.755 --> 52:42.782
[Whistle Blows]

52:42.859 --> 52:45.089
[Horn Blasts]

54:39.142 --> 54:41.235
<i>[Mann's Voice]</i>
<i>Oh, boy. </i>

55:45.975 --> 55:49.911
[Gearing Down]

56:00.156 --> 56:02.215
<i>[Coyote Howls]</i>

56:05.895 --> 56:09.058
Hi.
Help you, mister?

56:09.132 --> 56:12.067
You got a telephone?
Out in back.

56:12.135 --> 56:15.866
This way?
Something for your car?

56:15.939 --> 56:18.669
Uh, well, you can, uh...

56:18.742 --> 56:22.200
put what Ethyl you can
get in the tank.
All righty.

56:27.584 --> 56:31.111
Would you mind checking
those radiator hoses?
I'll do that.

56:31.187 --> 56:34.918
Take a look at my snakes
if you have time.

56:38.161 --> 56:41.096
[Snakes Rattling, Hissing]

56:43.400 --> 56:46.062
Weird place
for a telephone booth.

56:55.845 --> 56:59.508
Operator.
I'd like to report a truck driver
that's been endangering my life.

56:59.582 --> 57:04.019
In that case, I'll have to
give you the police, sir.
Right. Give me the police.

57:04.087 --> 57:08.353
Sir, which department
do you want?
Whichever's closer.

57:08.425 --> 57:13.158
What number are you
calling from?
Uh, this number is 982 1.

57:13.229 --> 57:15.891
[Snakes Rattling]

57:15.965 --> 57:18.195
[Engine Starts Up]

57:18.268 --> 57:20.793
[Brakes Decompress]

57:31.548 --> 57:33.948
[Man]
What's your name, sir?
David Mann.

57:34.017 --> 57:37.418
How do you spell that,
please?
M-A-N-N. That's two "N"s.

57:40.156 --> 57:42.283
<i>[Truck Engine</i>
<i>Accelerating]</i>
I'd like to report...

57:42.358 --> 57:45.054
a truck driver that's
been endangering my life.

57:45.128 --> 57:47.892
Your name again?
David Mann.

57:47.964 --> 57:52.992
[Horn Blasting]

57:53.069 --> 57:57.870
[Horn Blasting]

58:00.610 --> 58:02.510
Why'd he do that?

58:02.579 --> 58:05.173
Why'd he break
my cages up?

58:05.248 --> 58:11.153
[Horn Blasting]

58:29.239 --> 58:34.700
[Horn Blasting]

58:34.777 --> 58:36.711
<i>Why'd he break</i>
<i>my cages up? </i>

58:36.779 --> 58:38.713
Call the police!
With what?

58:38.781 --> 58:40.908
